parameters: \c[3]??? \c[0]Do you remember me? I visited your school for an interview half a year ago. You welcomed me back then.
\c[3]??? \c[0]I will be teaching here tomorrow onwards.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Yeah. You should go home, it’s late.
\c[2]Tian Fangfang \c[0]I didn't pay attention in class, so my punishment is to copy the text...
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Fangfang, let me show you something.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Close your eyes first, then open them when I tell you to.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Fangfang, you can open your eyes now.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Fangfang, have you played this before?
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Okay, I drew faces on every side inside. If you pick the side with the \c[1]smiling face\c[0], you are free to go.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Then let me go over the rules.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]You can pick a direction from \c[1]East, South, West and North\c[0], then you'll say\c[1] a number\c[0].
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]For example, if you pick East and 6, I'll move 6 times, then see what is drawn on the 'East' side.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]I drew faces on every side inside. If you pick the \c[1]smiling face\c[0], then you're off the hook.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]How does that sound? Choose a direction first.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Okay, let me see what it is.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Stop copying and go home, Fangfang.
\c[2]Tian Fangfang \c[0]but...\.\.Ms. Xu told me to do it...

\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Don't worry, I'll be your new Chinese literature teacher tomorrow,
I have the final say!
\c[2]Tian Fangfang \c[0]Ms. Chen...\.\.Can you teach me how to make this?
\c[2]Tian Fangfang \c[0]It looks like a star when it's opened, it's beautiful.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]A star...\.\.That's a very interesting analogy, I like it!
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]First, fold it up like this...
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]The last step is to open it up...
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]Look, this is it. Now you try, Fangfang.
\c[3]Chen Qingsui \c[0]You learn fast, let's fold more.
